<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Beautiful Web Page</title>
</head>
<body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; background: #f4f4f4; color: #333; margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box;">

    <header style="background: #333; color: #fff; padding: 1rem 0; text-align: center;">
        <h1 style="margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Welcome to My Beautiful Page</h1>
        <nav>
            <ul style="list-style: none; padding: 0; margin: 0;">
                <li style="display: inline; margin: 0 0.5rem;">
                    <a href="#home" style="color: #fff; text-decoration: none; font-weight: bold;">Home</a>
                </li>
                <li style="display: inline; margin: 0 0.5rem;">
                    <a href="#about" style="color: #fff; text-decoration: none; font-weight: bold;">About</a>
                </li>
                <li style="display: inline; margin: 0 0.5rem;">
                    <a href="#services" style="color: #fff; text-decoration: none; font-weight: bold;">Services</a>
                </li>
                <li style="display: inline; margin: 0 0.5rem;">
                    <a href="#contact" style="color: #fff; text-decoration: none; font-weight: bold;">Contact</a>
                </li>
            </ul>
        </nav>
    </header>

    <main style="max-width: 800px; margin: 2rem auto; padding: 1rem; background: #fff; box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);">
        <section id="home" style="margin-bottom: 2rem;">
            <h2 style="margin-bottom: 0.5rem; color: #333; border-bottom: 2px solid #333; display: inline-block; padding-bottom: 0.25rem;">Home</h2>
            <p>This is the home section of the page. It looks amazing!</p>
        </section>
        <section id="about" style="margin-bottom: 2rem;">
            <h2 style="margin-bottom: 0.5rem; color: #333; border-bottom: 2px solid #333; display: inline-block; padding-bottom: 0.25rem;">About</h2>
            <p>This is the about section of the page. Here, you can learn more about us.</p>
        </section>
        <section id="services" style="margin-bottom: 2rem;">
            <h2 style="margin-bottom: 0.5rem; color: #333; border-bottom: 2px solid #333; display: inline-block; padding-bottom: 0.25rem;">Services</h2>
            <p>This is the services section of the page. We offer various services to cater to your needs.</p>
        </section>
        <section id="contact" style="margin-bottom: 2rem;">
            <h2 style="margin-bottom: 0.5rem; color: #333; border-bottom: 2px solid #333; display: inline-block; padding-bottom: 0.25rem;">Contact</h2>
            <p>This is the contact section of the page. Feel free to reach out to us.</p>
        </section>
    </main>

    <footer style="text-align: center; padding: 1rem 0; background: #333; color: #fff;">
        <p style="margin: 0;">&copy; 2024 Beautiful Web Page. All rights reserved.</p>
    </footer>

</body>
</html>
